description: Bottle Lid. Uniquely shaped vessels add an intriguing appeal to anything from water, to dressings, to secret ingredients at the table or bar. Enhance your food & beverage service with the timeless, classic appeal of Bormioli Rocco Fido Jars and Bottles.. Customize any of these bottles and jars by using the chalkboard labels or have your companys logo etched in the side. FREE ETCHING FOR NEW INSTALLATIONS ON BORMIOLI ROCCO GLASSWARE. Customize your glass with your logo or pour line and create a fast economical way to elevate your beverage service while controlling your profits. These vessels have a tight seal to achieve health & safety objectives and have the ability to be customized with your company logo to create an even more unique occasion.
